metadata.name: Jengascoin DAO Token
metadata.description: Jengascoin DAO Tokens are your key to connecting and deriving value from the Jengscoin Blockchain Project. Token holders will have the ability to participate in governance and direction of the Jengascoin Blockchain Project. Upon mainnet launch of the Jengascoin Blockchain, network fees will be distributed to Jengascoin DAO Token holders.
